{
  "texts": [
    "• If not, can LLMs themselves be adapted to detect such disinformation?",
    "• How effective is DELD in detecting evolving LLMgenerated disinformation?",
    "A. DatasetsWe utilize an recent LLM-generated disinformation dataset [6], which includes a variety of disinformation generated by state-of-the-art LLMs such as ChatGPT [2], LLaMA [3], and Vicuna [40].",
    "This dataset provides a diverse and comprehensive range of disinformation examples, enabling extensive experimentation to address our research questions.",
    "In addition, we incorporate a human-written disinformation dataset [41] to better simulate the evolving nature of real-world disinformation."
  ]
}